The paper deals with developing new algorithms and methods for knowledge graph processing and relational learning using WikiData, which is a large open-source knowledge graph. This topic falls under several sub-categories of computer science, including databases (cs.DB), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), and computational linguistics (cs.CL).
